strings.Value: "Thank you, Ilora. I will need every sword. In this battle everything is at stake."
"I have no need of you. Take your people and leave."
"None of your business. Get out while you still can!"
"I changed my mind. We'll keep to our arrangement. Prepare for battle."

"Ah, here you are. Came to do away with the scoundrel, right? I gathered what's left of {d|c51 Ilora Lives}the River Razors{/d}. We are few, but every one of us dreams of gutting Irovetti! We will commence on your signal!"
"Pff. Crazy, are you? Well, whatever you say!"
"I know, I know. Heads will roll today, and with Hanspur's blessing, they won't be ours!"
"Well, are you ready? My fellows are gathering near the palace."
